data.title: Identify your iPhone model
data.meta_description: Find out how to identify your iPhone model by its model number and other details.
data.text:
Find out how to identify your iPhone model by its model number and other details.

Find the model number

Find out how to find the model number of your iPhone. Then find the model number in the list below.
